<quantity box="[815,915,884,908]" metricMagnitude="1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.75" metricValueMax="6.4" metricValueMin="1.1" pageId="181" pageNumber="182" unit="m" value="37.5" valueMax="64.0" valueMin="11.0">11–64 m</quantity>
, rarely cast ashore after storms.
</paragraph>
